eadiness,</span></div></div>"},{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 800\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">RAP Architecture — Full Stack Breakdown</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ LAYER 1: UI ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"70\" width=\"920\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"93\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">1. UI / Presentation Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"113\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">SAP Fiori Elements · Freestyle UI5 · OData V4 Client · Web APIs</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"65\" y1=\"125\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"155\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"145\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">OData V4 Request</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ LAYER 2: Service ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"160\" width=\"920\" height=\"60\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#E0F2FE\" stroke=\"#3B82F6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"183\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2563EB\">2. Service Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Service Definition → defines what entities are exposed</text>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"215\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Service Binding → binds to OData V4 UI or Web API protocol</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"65\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"250\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"240\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">EML (Entity Manipulation Language)</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ LAYER 3: Behavior ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"255\" width=\"920\" height=\"85\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"278\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">3. Behavior Layer</text>\n\n  <!-- Behavior operation boxes -->\n  <rect x=\"65\" y=\"290\" width=\"200\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"165\" y=\"308\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Behavior Definition (BDEF)</text>\n  <text x=\"165\" y=\"322\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">create / update / delete</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"285\" y=\"290\" width=\"200\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"308\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Behavior Implementation</text>\n  <text x=\"385\" y=\"322\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">ABAP class (local)</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"505\" y=\"290\" width=\"200\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"605\" y=\"308\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Draft Handling</text>\n  <text x=\"605\" y=\"322\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">Draft tables (if active)</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"725\" y=\"290\" width=\"200\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEF9C3\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"825\" y=\"308\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Authorization Control</text>\n  <text x=\"825\" y=\"322\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">%control / instance auth</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"65\" y1=\"340\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"370\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"360\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#E95420\">reads from</text>\n\n  <!-- ============ LAYER 4: Data Model ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"375\" width=\"920\" height=\"85\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"398\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">4. Data Model Layer</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"65\" y=\"410\" width=\"220\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEE2E2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"175\" y=\"428\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">CDS View Entity (Root)</text>\n  <text x=\"175\" y=\"442\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">define root view entity</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"305\" y=\"410\" width=\"220\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEE2E2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"415\" y=\"428\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">CDS Projection View</text>\n  <text x=\"415\" y=\"442\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">define root view entity (projection)</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"545\" y=\"410\" width=\"220\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEE2E2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"655\" y=\"428\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">Metadata Extension</text>\n  <text x=\"655\" y=\"442\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">@MetadataExtension: true</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"785\" y=\"410\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#FEE2E2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"855\" y=\"428\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">RAP BO</text>\n  <text x=\"855\" y=\"442\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">Business Object</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"65\" y1=\"460\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"490\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- ============ LAYER 5: Database ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"495\" width=\"920\" height=\"55\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"518\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">5. Database Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"65\" y=\"538\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">SAP HANA · DDIC Tables · Table Functions · AMDP · ABAP SQL via Open SQL</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"65\" y1=\"550\" x2=\"65\" y2=\"580\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- ============ FULL REQUEST FLOW ============ -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"585\" width=\"920\" height=\"200\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"610\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">RAP Request Flow — End to End</text>\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"618\" x2=\"940\" y2=\"618\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"642\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">Step</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"642\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">Component</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"642\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748B\">What Happens</text>\n  <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"648\" x2=\"900\" y2=\"648\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"668\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">1</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"668\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fiori / UI5</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"668\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">User triggers a request (list report, object page, action)</text>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"688\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#22C55E\">2</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"688\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Service Binding</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"688\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">OData V4 URL → maps to Service Definition entities</text>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"708\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">3</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"708\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Behavior Definition</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"708\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">EML → routes to create/update/delete or query implementation</text>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"728\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EAB308\">4</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"728\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Behavior Implementation</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"728\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">ABAP class: FOR MODIFY / FOR READ methods execute logic</text>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"748\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#EF4444\">5</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"748\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">CDS View Entity</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"748\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">SQL statement generated from CDS → Open SQL → HANA</text>\n\n  <text x=\"80\" y=\"768\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#A855F7\">6</text>\n  <text x=\"200\" y=\"768\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">SAP HANA</text>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"768\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Data returned to EML → serialized to OData V4 JSON → Fiori</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"managed implementation in class ZCL_RAP_TRAVEL unique;\nstrict ( 2 );\nwith draft;\n\ndefine behavior for ZPRAC_CDS_VIEW_ENTITY alias Travel\npersistent table /dmo/travel\nlock master\nauthorization master ( instance )\n{\n  field ( readonly : update ) TravelId, Createdby, Createdat;\n  field ( mandatory ) AgencyId, CustomerId, BeginDate, EndDate;\n  create;\n  update;\n  delete;\n\n  action ( features : instance ) acceptBooking result [1] $self;\n\n  mapping for /dmo/travel\n  {\n    TravelId = travel_id;\n    AgencyId = agency_id;\n    CustomerId = customer_id;\n    BeginDate = begin_date;\n    EndDate = end_date;\n  }\n}\n\ndefine behavior for ZPRAC_CDS_ASSOCIATION alias Booking\npersistent table /dmo/booking\nlock dependent by _Travel\n{\n  update;\n  delete;\n  association _Travel;\n}"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_RAP_BEHAVIOR-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Behavior definition (BDEF) is the RAP contract — it defines</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Managed implementation: the RAP framework generates all</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`with draft` enables draft-capable transactional UIs —</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>CRUD operations (create / update / delete) are declared per</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`implementation in class ZCL_... unique` binds the behavior</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Validations check data consistency before save (e.g., dates,</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Actions are custom operations: instance actions operate on</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>`strict ( 2 )` enforces modern RAP rules (cloud-readiness,</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_RAP_BEHAVIOR-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 800\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <